Errors:
    1. Compile (Syntax)
    2. Run time (User end)
    3. Logical (2+3 = 6)

Functions/Methods(inside a class):
    Why? --> readable, testable, reusable
    Types of functions:
        1. In-built --> print(), input()
        2. User defined --> default, parameter

    Parts of Functions:
        1. function call
        2. function body
        3. function definition


Loops: (run same command multiple times)
    For:
        for i in range(0,10): // for(int i = 0, i <= 10, i++)
            print(i)  //0,1
            i = i - 10 // 0

        when u have the end point and we need to execute every iterator

    While:
        i = 10
        while(i != 0):
            print(i)
            i = i - 10


